# How to publish new version:
1. Get current version in [manifest.json](mdc:app/manifest.json)
2. Increment version (by default, change patch version)
3. Update version in [manifest.json](mdc:app/manifest.json) and [popup.html](mdc:app/pages/popup.html).
4. Update [CHANGELOG.md](mdc:CHANGELOG.md).
5. Commit. Push git tag (sample: v1.1.1).

